The following Snippet Attempts to create the directory tree at path, and only suppresses the OSError with errno.EEXIST (meaning it already exists), re-raising any other error. Snippet: try:
    os.makedirs(path)
except OSError as exception:
    if (exception.errno != errno.EEXIST):
        raise .

